txt.en: 'Don't you go thinking times are different. Folk around here been gossiping since I was a girl.'
'All the hobbits around here ought to have something better to do than go sticking their noses in other folk's business.'
'Oh, how I love the white hills at sunset....'
'Have you been up to Town Hole to see Mayor Whitfoot? He's such a nice, young hobbit.'
